《'''爱的枷锁'''》（{{lang-en|''Chains of Love''}}）是2001年4至5月在[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]共播出六期的约会游戏节目，根据荷兰电视剧改编，主要内容是每个成年人（称为“挑选者”）与四名异性用锁链绑起来并一起生活四天四夜。挑选者能拿到一万美元，并有三次解开一名异性的机会，挑选者可以向被解开（淘汰）的异性补偿现金。等到只剩一名异性时，挑选者可以选择两人平分剩下的钱，也能自行保留。六期节目均由美国[[名流|电视名人]]麦迪逊·米歇尔主持。

《爱的枷锁》本是[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]订购的节目，后由联合派拉蒙电视网接手，希望通过开播更多无剧本节目提升电视台收视成绩，部分媒体认为本剧是[[真人实境节目|真人实境节目]]复兴的产物。大卫·加芬克尔是《爱的枷锁》的[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]，他还曾制作同类节目《[[相亲_(美国电视剧)|相亲]]》。

联合派拉蒙电视网在节目开播前针对年轻女子展开为期一个月的网上宣传。《爱的枷锁》起初占有[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]周二晚八点档，电视台打算将节目办成模拟逃犯追踪剧《[[追捕_(2001年电视剧)|追捕]]》的姐妹篇。部分媒体认为，《爱的枷锁》在[[电视联播网|电视联播网]]播映导致内容受限。评论界对本剧意见不一，评论员将其结构和基调与其他参赛者寻找情侣的节目对比，如《相亲》、《[[约会游戏|约会游戏]]》。《爱的枷锁》从未发行[[数码多功能影音光盘|数码多功能影音光盘]]和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]，也没有推出[[流媒体|流媒体]]。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:ChainsofLoveInChainsofLove.jpg|thumb]]

每期《爱的枷锁》都有五名参赛者来到加利福尼亚州[[帕洛斯弗迪斯庄园|帕洛斯弗迪斯庄园]]生活，身着制服和太阳镜的肌肉男扮成“锁链大师”，在“仪式室”用1.8米的锁链把所有参赛者手脚绑在一起<ref name="Source1">{{cite news | url = https://ew.com/article/2001/03/29/exclusive-peek-upns-chains-love/ | title = An exclusive peek at UPN's ''Chains of Love'' | last = Snierson | first = Dan | date = 2001-03-29 | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402161523/https://ew.com/article/2001/03/29/exclusive-peek-upns-chains-love/ | archivedate = 2019-04-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Source4">{{cite news | url = https://www.newsweek.com/when-chains-love-become-chain-fools-150021 | title = When 'Chains Of Love' Become A Chain Of Fools | last = Peyser | first = Marc  | date = 2001-04-15 | journal = [[新闻周刊|Newsweek]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402105305/https://www.newsweek.com/when-chains-love-become-chain-fools-150021 | archivedate = 2019-04-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Source2" />。拍摄期间，各参赛者之间的距离最大也只有约60厘米<ref name="Source9">{{cite web | archive-date = 2019-04-02 | first = Mike | deadurl = no | url = https://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/Chains-of-Love-is-no-ratings-lock-2013633.php | title = 'Chains of Love' is no ratings lock | last = McDaniel | date = 2001-04-16 | newspaper = [[休斯敦纪事报|Houston Chronicle]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402112714/https://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/Chains-of-Love-is-no-ratings-lock-2013633.php}}</ref>，但锁住参赛者的镜头没有在节目中播出<ref name="Source2">{{cite web | url = https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/A-Match-Made-in-Infamy-UPN-hits-new-low-with-2931006.php | title = A Match Made in Infamy / UPN hits new low with 'Chains of Love' | last = Carman | first = John | date = 2001-04-17 | newspaper = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402105936/https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/A-Match-Made-in-Infamy-UPN-hits-new-low-with-2931006.php | archive-date = 2019-04-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

五名参赛者包括“挑选者”和四名相互竞争的“玩伴”<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source3">{{cite news | url = http://old.post-gazette.com/tv/20010417owen2.asp | title = Reality TV sinks further under 'Chains of Love' | last = Owen | first = Rob | date = 2001-04-17 | newspaper = [[匹兹堡邮报|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] | archivedate = 2018-07-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701165026/http://old.post-gazette.com/tv/20010417owen2.asp}}</ref>。挑选者此前已经给出心目中理想结婚对象的条件，电视台依照这些条件采访参赛者，根据回答选出四人与挑选者一起参加节目<ref name="Source9" />。挑选者男女均有，玩伴一定是挑选者的异性<ref name="Source25">{{cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/chains-of-love/episodes/200437/ | title = Episode Guide | work = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190402111549/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/chains-of-love/episodes/200437/ | archive-date = 2019-04-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。五人被绑在一起四天四夜，还需完成购物、做饭、溜冰等日常任务<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source9" />。各人也有部分时间保有隐私，如上厕所、洗澡、换衣服等<ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source3" />。

挑选者在每期节目开始时拿到一万美元现金，能凭个人喜好向其他参赛者赠送现金<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" />。挑选者还有三次淘汰竞争玩伴的权力，每次可淘汰一人，锁链大师会解开被淘汰者<ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source2" />。挑选者有权决定是否向被淘汰者赠送部分现金<ref name="Source2" />，只剩一名玩伴时如果两人都觉得已经建立“爱的连接”就能分掉剩余现金<ref name="Source1" />，也可由挑选者保留<ref name="Source2" />。最后的玩伴可以拒绝与挑选者关系更进一步<ref name="Source9" />。

== 制作 ==
[[File:MadisonMicheleTVGuide_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]

《爱的枷锁》根据荷兰电视剧改编<ref name="Source1" />，由荷兰[[恩德莫|恩德莫]]（{{lang|en|Endemol}}）公司制作<ref name="BooksNetherlands">{{cite book | last1 = Magder | first = Ted | chapter = Television 2.0: The Business of American Television in Transition | title = Reality TV: Remaking Television Culture | editor-last1 = Murray | editor-first1 = Susan | editor-last2 = Ouellette | editor-first2 = Laurie | year = 2004 | publisher = NYU Press | location = New York | pages = 144 | isbn = 978-0814757345 | url = https://archive.org/details/realitytvremakin00susa | accessdate = 2020-08-28}}</ref>，曾制作美国约会游戏节目《相亲》（''{{lang|en|Blind Date}}''）的大卫·加芬克尔（{{lang|en|David Garfinkle}}）任[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]<ref name="Source1" />，澳大利亚、荷兰、美国和英国均买下格式版权<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.c21media.net/chained-returns-to-e4/ | title = Chained returns to E4 | first = Ed | last = Waller | date = 2002-02-22 | accessdate = 2020-08-28 | archive-date = 2020-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828104914/https://www.c21media.net/chained-returns-to-e4/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[真人實境節目|真人實境節目]]《[[名人老大哥_(電視節目)|名人老大哥]]》的部分开发人员参与本剧制作<ref name="Books7">{{cite book | last1 = Brooks | first1 = Tim | last2 = Marsh | first2 = Earle F. | title = The Complete Directory to Prime Time Network and Cable TV Shows, 1946–Present | year = 2009 | publisher = Random House Publishing Group | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-345-49773-4 | ref = brooksmarsh2009 | page = 888}}</ref>。加芬克尔自称开播后也不知道节目会如何发展，参赛者之间的竞争开始变得就像《[[飞越情海|飞越情海]]》（{{lang|en|''Melrose Place''}}）之类[[肥皂剧|肥皂剧]]<ref name="Source1" />。六期节目均由美国[[名流|电视名人]]麦迪逊·米歇尔（{{lang|en|Madison Michele}}）主持<ref name="SourceGuide">{{cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/chains-of-love/cast/200437/ | title = Cast | work = TV Guide | publisher = CBS Interactive | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171006062659/http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/chains-of-love/cast/200437/ | archivedate = 2017-10-06}}</ref>。

《爱的枷锁》本是[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]订购的节目<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source7">{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2001/01/08/business/in-television-s-new-reality-temptation-puts-vows-to-the-test.html | title = In Television's New Reality, Temptation Puts Vows to the Test | last = Carter | first = Bill | date = 2001-01-08 | newspaper = The New York Times | archivedate = 2018-07-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701194112/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/01/08/business/in-television-s-new-reality-temptation-puts-vows-to-the-test.html}}</ref>，计划请恩德莫制作九期，节目名称待称<ref name="Source14247">{{cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/news/matt-kunitz-interview-1035705/ | title = Wipeout and 101 Ways Producer Matt Kunitz on His Reality Lessons | last = Schneider | first = Michael | date = 2011-07-26 | work = TV Guide | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181130190905/https://www.tvguide.com/news/matt-kunitz-interview-1035705/ | archivedate = 2018-11-30}}</ref>。但因制作人之间存在创作理念分歧，全国广播公司最终决定放弃<ref name="Source142">{{cite web | url = https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=111201 | title = Fox's Temptation Island Draws Fire | date = 2001-01-08 | publisher = ABC News | archivedate = 2018-07-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180702011043/https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/story?id=111201}}</ref>。《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》的马克·佩瑟（{{lang|en|Marc Peyser}}）认为，全国广播公司是因为“道德因素”退出项目<ref name="Source4" />。该公司最后将荷兰电视节目《把握现在或梦中再见》（{{lang|en|''Now or Neverland''}}）改编成《[[勇敢者的游戏_(电视剧)|勇敢者的游戏]]》（''{{lang|en|Fear Factor}}''），代替《爱的枷锁》<ref name="Source14247" />。计划开播更多无剧本节目提升收视率的[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]接手项目，并与另外三档真人实境节目共同制作<ref name="Source6">{{cite web | url = https://nypost.com/2001/03/22/a-reality-mentality-upn-pumps-out-eight-unscripted-strike-beaters/ | title = A Reality Mentality UPN Pumps Out Eight Unscripted Strike Beaters | last = Kaplan | first = Don | date = 2001-03-22 | newspaper = New York Post | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701194238/https://nypost.com/2001/03/22/a-reality-mentality-upn-pumps-out-eight-unscripted-strike-beaters/ | archivedate = 2018-07-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的比尔·卡特（{{lang|en|Bill Carter}}）认为，真人实境竞争节目《[[幸存者_(美国电视剧)|幸存者]]》（''{{lang|en|Survivor}}''）掀起“第二波真人实境节目”热潮，《爱的枷锁》便是其中推波助澜的一员。在他看来，这些真人实境节目“旨在突破黄金时段电视”的内容限制。<ref name="Source7" />金伯利·贝尔（{{lang|en|Kimberly K. Bell}}）通过2007年的著作指出，《爱的枷锁》制作模式接近《幸存者》 ，两个节目都以“精心构建的运动场”为背景，制作人都会修改参赛者的身份进一步迎合观众喜好<ref name="Books5">{{cite book | last = Bell | first = Kimberly K. | chapter = Models of (Im)perfection | title = Cultural Studies of the Modern Middle Ages | editor-last1 = Joy | editor-first1 = E. | editor-last2 = Bell | editor-first2 = K. | editor-last3 = Ramsey | editor-first3 = M. | editor-last4 = Seaman | editor-first4 = M. | year = 2007 | publisher = Springer | location = New York | isbn = 978-1-349-53432-6 | ref = Bell2007 | pages = 26, 30}}</ref>。

联合派拉蒙电视网高管认为，无剧本节目热潮的兴起一方面是因为制作成本低于有剧本节目，另一方面也因这类节目更受年轻观众青睐。电视网总裁迪恩·瓦伦丁（{{lang|en|Dean Valentine}}）称：“从社会角度来看，要让观众、特别是年轻观众认同虚构剧情的难度越来越大，他们怎么看都觉得很虚假。<ref name="Source7" />电视网娱乐总监汤姆·努南（{{lang|en|Tom Nunan}}）表示，《爱的枷锁》旨在提升电视台收视率，观众明显不喜欢千篇一律的电视节目，所以对活动节目往往青眼有加。<ref name="Source6" />

瓦伦丁称，节目名称中的“枷锁”意指“人类情感纽带”。在他看来，《爱的枷锁》很大程度上属于[[肢体喜剧|肢体喜剧]]（{{lang|en|physical comedy}}）<ref name="Source7" />，与[[性虐恋|性虐恋]]没有直接联系<ref name="Source1" />。瓦伦丁还认为，本剧的卖点不限于性魅力，参赛者一起兑变，因为他们都必须面对接受与拒绝、恐惧和需求，节目过程情绪感染力十足，观众仿佛置身[[艾哈德研讨训练班|艾哈德研讨训练班]]般难以抗拒<ref name="Source4" />。

