== 播映 ==
[[2000－2001年美国电视网节目表|2000－2001年美国电视网节目]]季中换血期间，联合派拉蒙电视网共推出三档新剧，除《爱的枷锁》外，另外两档分别是《[[特别小组2|特别小组2]]》（''{{lang|en|Special Unit 2}}''）和《[[所有的灵魂|所有的灵魂]]》<ref name="Source5">{{cite web | url = https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/9312/upn-chains-of-love.html | title = UPN Chains of Love | last = Liebeskind | first = Ken | date = 2001-04-03 | publisher = MediaPost Communications | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200823111008/https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/9312/upn-chains-of-love.html | archivedate = 2020-08-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《爱的枷锁》起初占据[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]周二晚八点档<ref name="News1">{{cite news | title = UPN loves its 'Chains' | date = 2001-04-02 | work = Broadcasting & Cable | page = 18 | author = Joe Schlosser | url = https://www.nexttv.com/news/upn-loves-its-chains-96839 | accessdate = 2020-08-28 | archive-date = 2020-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200828105010/https://www.nexttv.com/news/upn-loves-its-chains-96839 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，第一期在2001年4月17日播出<ref name="Source1" />。联合派拉蒙电视网起初打算将本剧作为模拟逃犯追踪剧《[[追捕_(2001年电视剧)|追捕]]》（''{{lang|en|Manhunt}}''）的姐妹篇，该剧主要讲述逃犯摆脱赏金猎人追捕，逃犯和猎人都是演员假扮<ref name="Source12">{{cite web | title = UPN's Virtual Reality Issue Scenes reshot for 'Manhunt' | last = Huff | first = Richard | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/upn-virtual-reality-issue-scenes-reshot-manhunt-article-1.930565 | date = 2001-08-17 | newspaper = New York Daily News | archive-date = 2018-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180707005926/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/upn-virtual-reality-issue-scenes-reshot-manhunt-article-1.930565}}</ref>。《爱的枷锁》曾与《所有的灵魂》搭配播出<ref name="Source3" />，但《所有的灵魂》仅两集后就暂时停播<ref name="Source42">{{cite news | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2001-04-30-0104300212-story.html | title = UPN pulls 'All Souls' after just two shows | date = 2001-04-30 | newspaper = Chicago Tribune | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701165203/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2001-04-30/features/0104300212_1_upn-chicago-hope-scott-bakula | archivedate = 2018-08-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

联合派拉蒙电视网在节目开播前开展长达一个月的网上宣传，广告在{{lang|en|Targetmatch.com}}、{{lang|en|Madhive.com}}和{{lang|en|Ecrush.com}}旗下网站刊登，主要面向12至34岁女观众。[[瑪瑞娜戴爾瑞_(加利福尼亞州)|玛瑞娜戴尔瑞]]的{{lang|en|L}}90[[市场营销|营销公司]]曾为联合派拉蒙电视网宣传电视剧《[[加里和迈克|加里和迈克]]》（''{{lang|en|Gary & Mike}}''），《爱的枷锁》也由该司负责宣传。{{lang|en|L}}90营销副总载劳伦·凯（{{lang|en|Lauren Kay}}）自称为节目制订“简单明了的品牌计划”，具体手段包括[[弹出式广告|弹出式广告]]、[[Flash动画|Flash动画]]，以及利用[[微型网站|微型网站]]完成的抽奖活动。<ref name="Source5" />

部分媒体认为，节目在[[电视联播网|电视联播网]]播出可能导致内容受限<ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source2" />。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的约翰·卡曼（{{lang|en|John Carman}}）就举出剧中令人莫名其妙的桥段为例，上一个镜头是挑选者向四名女子提议在热水溶缸[[裸泳|裸泳]]，结果下一个镜头众人就都已穿上泳装<ref name="Source2" />。佩瑟感觉剧中情色内容程度与《[[恋爱时代_(美国电视剧)|恋爱时代]]》差不多，觉得不及他起初想象的那么露骨<ref name="Source4" />。

《爱的枷锁》仅播出六期就被联合派拉蒙电视网取消<ref name="Source8">{{cite journal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200619125843/https://variety.com/2001/tv/features/upn-deals-for-roswell-benches-vet-moesha-1117799599/ | url = https://variety.com/2001/tv/features/upn-deals-for-roswell-benches-vet-moesha-1117799599/ | title = UPN deals for 'Roswell', benches vet 'Moesha' | last = Schneider | first = Michael | date = 2001-05-16 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archivedate = 2020-06-19 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Source10">{{cite news | url = http://old.post-gazette.com/tv/20010518networks.asp | title = 'Fox puts superhero comedy up against CBS juggernaut | last = Owen | first = Rob | date = 2001-05-18 | newspaper = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181215123642/http://old.post-gazette.com/tv/20010518networks.asp | archivedate = 2018-12-15 | accessdate = 2018-12-15}}</ref>，此后一直没有发行[[数码多功能影音光盘|数码多功能影音光盘]]和[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]，也没有推出[[流媒体|流媒体]]<ref name="SourceHomeRelease">{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-02-11 | deadurl = yes | publisher = TVShowsOnDVD.com | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Chains-Love/9848 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180211065211/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Chains-Love/9848 | title = Chains of Love (2001)}}</ref>。节目取消后，[[威廉·夏特纳|威廉·夏特纳]]和迪恩·瓦伦丁在[[麦迪逊广场花园|麦迪逊广场花园]]出席活动时恶搞《爱的枷锁》，两人被锁链绑在一起<ref name="Books3">{{cite book | last1 = Caldwell | first1 = John Thornton | title = Production Culture: Industrial Reflexivity and Critical Practice in Film and Television | year = 2008 | publisher = Duke University Press | location = Durham, NC | isbn = 978-0-8223-4111-6 | ref = Caldwell2008 | page = 100}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
《爱的枷锁》面世后评价不佳<ref name="SourceGuide" /><ref name="Source7" />，[[罗伯·欧文|罗伯·欧文]]（{{lang|en|Rob Owen}}）在《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》发文谴责节目构想堪称“电视卖淫”，是电视最恶劣行径的代表，观众甚至不能从中体会到做贼心虚的快感<ref name="Source3" />。《[[奥古斯塔纪事报|奥古斯塔纪事报]]》（''{{lang|en|The Augusta Chronicle}}''）发文，称本剧让联合派拉蒙电视网蒙羞<ref name="Source13">{{cite news | archivedate = 2017-10-06 | url = http://chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2002/02/18/ent_334102.shtml#.WdMOMxNSxE4 | title = 'Shipmates' sends couples over the bounding main | date = 2002-02-18 | newspaper = The Augusta Chronicle | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171006111817/http://chronicle.augusta.com/stories/2002/02/18/ent_334102.shtml}}</ref>。学者詹姆斯·布朗（{{lang|en|James W. Brown}}）2005年的著作《日间到黄金档：美国电视节目史》（{{lang|en|''From Daytime to Primetime: The History of American Television Programs''}}）声称，节目构思为情绪和肉体虐待创造条件<ref name="Books1">{{cite book | last = Roman | first1 = James W. | title = From Daytime to Primetime: The History of American Television Programs | url = https://archive.org/details/fromdaytimetopri00roma | year = 2005 | publisher = Greenwood Publishing Group | location = Westport | isbn = 978-0313319723 | ref = Roman2005 | page = [https://archive.org/details/fromdaytimetopri00roma/page/n206 178]}}</ref>。

部分评论员对本剧有更正面的看法<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" />卡曼一方面谴责节目伤害参赛者的尊严来吸引观众眼球，另一方面还是对每个男子处理局面的不同手段很感兴趣<ref name="Source2" />。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》刊登丹·斯尼森（{{lang|en|Dan Snierson}}）的文章，称赞《爱的枷锁》构思新颖，堪称“电视史上最离奇、最迷人的真人实境节目”<ref name="Source1" />。

许多评论将《爱的枷锁》与其他电视节目对比。布朗认为剧中通过强调两性关系来演示[[博弈论|博弈论]]，就像《[[约会游戏|约会游戏]]》（''{{lang|en|The Dating Game}}''）与《[[夜夜春宵|夜夜春宵]]》（''{{lang|en|Anything Goes}}''）结合的产物<ref name="Books1" />。佩瑟称，制作人把握的节目基调与《相亲》 一致<ref name="Source4" />。评论认为，后来的约会节目《[[恋爱达人|恋爱达人]]》（''{{lang|en|elimiDATE}}''）和《逃生共同体》（{{lang|en|''Tethered''}}）都曾借鉴《爱的枷锁》<ref name="Source17">{{cite news | url = https://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Buffy-s-out-Superman-s-in-as-The-WB-revamps-for-1054775.php | title = Buffy's out, Superman's in as The WB revamps for fall | last = Levesque | first = John | date = 2001-05-15 | newspaper = Seattle Post-Intelligencer | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180707011217/https://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Buffy-s-out-Superman-s-in-as-The-WB-revamps-for-1054775.php | archive-date = 2018-07-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Books5" /><ref name="SourceTethered">{{cite news | url = https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/234787/ties-that-bind-discoverys-tethered-revives-rea.html | title = Ties That Bind: Discovery's 'Tethered' Revives Reality-Show Memories | last = Buckman | first = Adam | date = 2014-09-24 | publisher = MediaPost Communications | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180706215115/https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/234787/ties-that-bind-discoverys-tethered-revives-rea.html | archivedate = 2018-07-06}}</ref>，特别是参赛者与四人约会<ref name="Source17" />或是将多人捆绑起来完成特殊任务的构想<ref name="Books5" /><ref name="SourceTethered" />。

